  "text": "1. The form of our proposed parametric noise-robust estimators (i.e. of volatility, high-frequency covariance, etc.) is much simpler than the form of i.i.d noise-robust alternatives, which are typically quite hard to implement (see, e.g., the pre-averaging method in [CITATION_1] ). 2. The estimators have faster rates of convergence. 3. It eases the analysis of the problem at hand.",
